name: 1920 (Ikkiel)
description:
1920 is a school project made with Unity3D from our team named Fathers Hatters Studio.

Composed by :

Adrien Bouyer (Bergermite)

Darry Ha (Ikkiel)

Guillaume Jurado

Lucas Valenti (Unikhorn)

Vincent Zemboulingame (ZicV)

Play as Dario “Don” Valenti, the new head of the Valenti family, who attacks different gangs to steal their influence and expand his own territory during the dark years of prohibition !
